{"tid":978434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他赴海外娶妻　還沒洞房「老婆就懷孕了」","createTime":"2019-01-12T02:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T04:08:36.000Z","uid":72009,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35d1b68d333bcffb7f4a64d25c6cdf81bc156c04","tid":978434,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T02:26:29.000Z","msg":"桃園一名黃姓男子1年多前透過婚姻仲介赴印尼娶老婆，相中一名女子，約定婚後來台同住。他返台沒多久即辦妥結婚登記，但妻子一直拒絕來台。<br />\n <br />\n黃男透過仲介打聽，得知妻子已懷孕，她傳簡訊給他「覺得和你結婚是一件後悔的事」、「我在台灣不能工作，你能給我什麼嗎？」黃無法接受被戴綠帽，去年3月向桃園地院訴請離婚。<br />\n <br />\n《聯合報》報導，黃男表示，他辦妥結婚手續，還沒洞房妻子卻懷孕了，很不諒解。婚姻介紹人作證，黃妻確實懷孕，也拒絕來台。法官判准離婚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190112/1499321/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190112%2F1499321%2F&d=AhD2ruAgsQXXYOHadUyRcNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=86b1f2cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190112%2F1499321%2F&h=a21a0190\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190112/1499321/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩未中出"},{"pid":"4469cf81653a41e9cf7298788ae510b3b7ed2708","tid":978434,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"women are g"}]}